---
<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
	<div class="profile-container">
		<div class="profile-image">
			<img src="public/test.jpeg" alt="Rohan Kamath">
		</div>
		<div class="profile-info">
			<h1>Rohan Kamath</h1>
			<p> 
				I am a Master's student in Computer Science at Syracuse University. I am research assistant at the 
				<a href="https://c4-lab.github.io/">C4 Lab</a> lead by Professor <a href="https://c4-lab.github.io/josh-introne/">Joshua Introne</a>.
				Here I am working on the <a href="https://c4-lab.github.io/belief-landscape/"> Belief Landscape Framework</a>, where my contributions
