				implementing DynGEM, attempting to improve upon the existing framework for better results.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b> I am currently looking for full time job opportunities for Fall 24, in the domains of software development and data science. </b>
				Please feel free to download my resume. You can send me an <a href="mailto:rkamath@syr.edu">email</a> to reach out to me. 
			</p>	
